name: Blade Bunny
description: In the forest on the south side of the capital of the kingdom the influence of the Litch created these ferocious, ruthless and cute creatures. "the Tome of monsters and beasts" describes the Blade Bunny as a very smart creature and as accustomed to living and hunting in groups, which does everything to kill the prey even use cunning stratagems, in fact there is no shortage of stories of adventurers who once attracted by a blade bunny that hid its tail were then attacked and stabbed by a pack of dozens of monsters. Someone say that they kill much more than they need to eat and that out of boredom they even go so far as to kill each other.
